graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks Component<br/>Workbench Images]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    Notebooks -->|"base OS & runtime"| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    Notebooks -->|"notebook IDE"| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4]
    Notebooks -->|"R IDE"| RStudioServer[RStudio Server]
    Notebooks -->|"VS Code IDE"| CodeServer[code-server]
    Notebooks -->|"cluster mgmt"| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift CLI - oc]
    Notebooks -->|"doc conversion"| Pandoc[Pandoc]
    Notebooks -->|"LaTeX rendering"| TeXLive[TeX Live]

    %% External Dependencies - GPU (Optional)
    Notebooks -.->|"GPU accel (optional)"| CUDA[CUDA 12.6/12.8/13.0]
    Notebooks -.->|"AMD GPU (optional)"| ROCM[ROCM 6.2/6.3/6.4]

    %% External Dependencies - ML Frameworks (Optional)
    Notebooks -.->|"ML framework (optional)"| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|"ML framework (optional)"| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|"deploys workbenches"| NotebookController[odh-notebook-controller]
    Notebooks -->|"displays images"| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    Notebooks -->|"authentication"| OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy sidecar]
    Notebooks -->|"pipeline execution"| KubeflowPipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>Elyra]
    Notebooks -->|"user data storage"| PVC[Persistent Volume Claims]
    Notebooks -->|"external access"| Routes[OpenShift Routes]

    %% Build Infrastructure
    Notebooks -->|"automated builds"| Konflux[Konflux CI/CD<br/>Tekton Pipelines]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    Notebooks -->|"package install"| PyPI[pypi.org<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -.->|"data access (user)"| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Notebooks -->|"cluster API"| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Container Registries
    Konflux -->|"publishes to"| QuayIO[quay.io/opendatahub]
    Konflux -->|"publishes to"| RedHatRegistry[registry.redhat.io]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|"reads"| ImageStreams[ImageStream Manifests]
    Konflux -->|"updates"| ImageStreams

